{"tid":1647692,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動]印尼政府唔做嘢！香港人聲援爆眼記者","createTime":"2019-10-12T00:44:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T12:04:48.000Z","uid":139474,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8df477087a1cfe0db641eb1705a1b87bb03a219a","tid":1647692,"uid":139474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T00:44:40.000Z","msg":"印尼記者喺香港採訪被警方射中致盲，印尼政府唔理，香港人一定要理，一齊推返單嘢上國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n長話短說，下星期六搞返次遊行聲援好冇！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">《追究警暴 守護記者》<br />\n日子：10月19日（星期六）<br />\n時間：1PM<br />\n地點：灣仔修頓-&gt;銅鑼灣印尼領事館</span></span><br />\n<br />\n琴日有印尼工人喺印尼領事館抗議，但得好少人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QiaBokp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQiaBokp.png&h=741817c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">印度政府無行動</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「主辦者之一的Sringatin表示，Veby遭到射擊後，<span style=\"color: red;\">印尼政府未有任何實際行動保護自己的國民</span>，令印尼移工感到憂心。她表示，印尼政府和港府和中國政府都有經濟往來，因而選擇忽略他們的遭遇，她表示憤怒。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">假消息抹黑印尼姐姐收錢遊行</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「自10月初網上開始流傳「印尼姐姐每日收3000元參與示威後被捕」的假消息，其後更<span style=\"color: red;\">有印尼領事館官員轉發</span>，警告在港印尼女工「你們什麼也不知道，別做多餘的事情。」Sringatin希望印尼政府可以澄清消息，並找出假消息來源，讓傳播假消息的人負上責任。」<br />\n<br />\n人哋嚟香港打工，報道畀印尼嘅人知香港發生咩事，都畀班狗搞到眼到盲埋，印尼唔理我哋香港人理！！一齊聲援印尼記者，遊行再諗方法眾籌，畀記者知道<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢哋唔係Condom!!!!!</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n*遊行地點可以再傾，揀灣仔係因為印尼記者中槍地點喺灣仔，去印尼領事館係要畀壓力印尼理呢單嘢順勢推上國際"},{"pid":"effe4c54fa9f45e4a4c395e5bb69cfa9f5b651ab","tid":1647692,"uid":139474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T00:45:01.000Z","msg":"咁早有冇人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57113110eb9fdbc3c24f3686ff9fc376390a8015","tid":1647692,"uid":139474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T00:45:51.000Z","msg":"我哋無唔記得印尼記者！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b250ff902e75cf1428eda04415d75adea82ad61","tid":1647692,"uid":97224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T00:46:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52154a404f103c6efd3b554434616bbca1c58bcc","tid":1647692,"uid":139474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T00:46:22.000Z","msg":"一個星期時間去宣傳行動"},{"pid":"c29c316af5c891027feb91f235cfea34fc5033bd","tid":1647692,"uid":248139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T00:46:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0072ea4dbf49bbaa234225c4731a15a0e48718a0","tid":1647692,"uid":139474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T00:46:36.000Z","msg":"聚到人啦掛"},{"pid":"6f33964d4281b50b94a5dfb4a38ee3db1a01893b","tid":1647692,"uid":139474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T00:46:50.000Z","msg":"Connect埋印尼姐姐一齊去"},{"pid":"430f53749a0d5e6a7eca31e38a74d80b85731e6e","tid":1647692,"uid":139474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T00:47:05.000Z","msg":"10連開始"},{"pid":"d8926623f2c1c724aecd1c279ef670840199ae60","tid":1647692,"uid":139474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T00:47:22.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"a83bc7d2f7b4fbb916876b4876b1393836e0bd9c","tid":1647692,"uid":139474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T00:47:37.000Z","msg":"2/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243c636ed3f90c27835950c1039c8dd50d5f6ba0","tid":1647692,"uid":139474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T00:47:49.000Z","msg":"3/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4686ec4871e2d1399ee940e6ec15753b7073e