,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T00:52:31.000Z","msg":"晏啲再推過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a76264725504db7aa5aecaa9f4f7bc044703c0e","tid":1647692,"uid":8730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T00:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PPncF38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPPncF38.jpg&h=a15ac423&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n出嚟呀 今日三點呀<br />\n<br />\n星期日 五區開花 <br />\n香港人自救</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"badf48a35eee38c187dddb9fec655ff46d664c6f","tid":1647692,"uid":42629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T06:03:28.000Z","msg":"去"},{"pid":"19860af322ebef1b6b780ddb3f721df876bce8ad","tid":1647692,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T06:07:21.000Z","msg":"初頭又話追究到底. 印尼政腐突然又笠水, 真係人都癲"},{"pid":"daf7b6aa69f70be3d58f42adb4b503fc08ab5c91","tid":1647692,"uid":139474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:25:02.000Z","msg":"推返出嚟先"}]}